To install on OS X
==================

Run `make install && make` to install to the ~/.apod directory, creating it if necessary.

Open the Desktop & Screen Saver preferences panel.
Add a new folder by clicking the add folder button.
Navigate to the ~/.apod directory by dragging the Finder proxy icon to the Add Folder panel.
Select the 'Astronomy_Picture_of_the_Day' file.

To uninstall on OS X
====================

make uninstall
